data.description: Assumable FHA 2.99% Mortgage! Open concept allows for easy interaction between the different living areas so you'll always feel connected to the heart of the home. Large kitchen island with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Upstairs, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms and a loft. The loft is a versatile area that can be used to suit your needs. Vaulted ceiling exude sophistication in the primary bedroom featuring a large walk in closet and ensuite bath. The lower level features a forth bedroom, large family room, full bath and ample storage space. Walk out to the fully fenced in backyard boasting a large stamped concrete patio perfect for entertaining. Heated and insulated attached two car garage. Come make lasting memories in this newer modern, spacious home.
